  <name>MiAZ</name>
  <summary>Personal Document Organizer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Possibility of using one or more document repositories. One at time. But it can be switched at any time.</li>
        <li>No database. The directory holding the documents is the database.</li>
        <li>Properties are extracted from the own filenames.</li>
    </ul>
